<br>
Discordant Melodies... This ability should have a moderate reuse timer (30 to 60 min) and should generate enough aggro to pull the mob off ANYONE, espescially since we can FM and drop the aggro to the next person on the list.  1 min duration is plenty.<br>
<br>
Now, this still does not address our desire to be jacks or jills of all trades and tank a normal LDoN with time gear or better.  We have hate REDUCING songs, but no hate INCREASING songs.  Implement a taunt song~  Put the aggro back on our chants.  The aggro was 'unintentionally removed,' so why not 'INTENTIONALLY PUT IT BACK PLZ.'<br>
<br>
Dance of Blades... Okay, it looks like this has been changed to a 100% dual wield and 21-42% increase in double attack.  Now I will have something to do when the guild leader calls offensive except to tap my bellows key furiously or to use my emote dps disc.<br>
<br>
Shield of Notes...  Good for raiders, limited usefulness otherwise.  The duration sucks, it's SELF ONLY atm, and costs buku AA.  I won't spend a single point in it as it stands.  Hi, Innate Wisdom.  Hi, Packrat.  Duration needs to increase or reuse decrease.  Seriously, how many guilds take 72 minutes to get to the next boss mob?  Thank god I'm not in one of them.  Shorten the reuse drastically and add a mana cost and I'd go for it.<br>
<br>
Evercraptastic Bellowing... It seems that Boastful Bellow is SoE's dead horse.  Keep on flogging it, fellas.  Eventually it'll do something useful.  I use it to pull and stun gaters (OMG, he channeled that one... let's see what happens in 18 sec... Wait, I'll just mez it.. no, it's a named mob and unmezzable.  Great.  TRAIN TO THE CLERIC!  LOADING, PLEASE WAIT...  Now, boastful bellow, from PoP, was EXCELLENT.  Great range, AWESOME for pulling.  okay, add in a level increase to make the stun portion more effective.  Moderate usefulness.  Why not also add a modifier to the resist check while you're at it?  Pulling in Qvic, I get a TON of resists on my bellows.  Now, the mobs still come, but I just lost ramp to the cleric. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :dieplz --><img src=http://members.cox.net/skoriksis/smilies/dieplz.gif ALT=":dieplz"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
As for the rest?  Keeping illusions while zoning seems purty spiffy, and will definitely help me to kill Tuna Muram Sandwich.  Worn regen increase... YES PLZ.  I love regen.  Worn FT increase... Possibly the best AA for a bard atm~  12 mana regen on muramite gear alone is GOOG.  The unconscious/death AA thingy... seems to me like a ghetto TotD.  joy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19697.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19697.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19697.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19697.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19697.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showMessageRange?topicID=19697.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a> <b>7</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showPrevMessage?topicID=19697.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showNextMessage?topicID=19697.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19697.topic&index=123><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.emailToFriend?topicID=19697.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Frien